rf Road, the Oworonsoki to Apapa, through Oshodi Road, and the Obajana-Kabba Road projects which were carried out by Dangote Group as well as the Bodo-Bonny bridges and road are some of the road infrastructure projects in Nigeria implemented under the Road Infrastructure Development and Refurbishment Investment Tax Credit Scheme. 85